BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:wEj6WikZEz1uUj9F__RTq
SUMMARY:Silent Reading Night
DTSTAMP:20260320T020834Z
DTSTART:20260319T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Silent Reading Night – March Edition \\nDate: Thursday\\\, Marc
	h 19th \\nTime: 6:00 PM – 9:00 PM \\nTheme: Pages Shared: A Community Book
	 Exchange \\nWe wanted to celebrate this month’s silent reading night with
	 a community book exchange themed reading night! Feathered Pages will be t
	abling for this event. \\nEvent Activities: \\nCommunity Book Swap \\nTo p
	articipate in the book swap\\\, let the front desk know upon arrival and r
	eceive your raffle ticket. One book = 1 ticket. Feel free to bring as many
	 books as you would like to swap! \\n\\nGrab some wrapping paper from the 
	front desk with a blank note card that answers one of these two prompts:\\
	n“Why I loved this book…” or “describe this book in a sentence..”\\nWrap u
	p the book and tape the note card to the cover with the answered prompt.\\
	nDrop books at categorized area on the stage\\n\\n\\nFiction\\nNonfiction\
	\nRomance\\nFantasy/Sci-Fi\\nMemoir\\nPoetry\\n\\nRaffle Announcement (at 
	8:30 PM) \\nThere will be up to 5 winners! The prize is a Hugo House tote 
	with books inside! \\n \\nEvent Itinerary \\n6:00 PM – Mix & Mingle \\n\\n
	Grab a cup of tea and settle in.\\nMeet fellow readers and share what book
	 you’re currently enjoying.\\nBYOM – Bring Your Own Mug! Hot water will be
	 available.\\n\\n6:30 PM – Silent Reading Begins \\n\\nSettle into your co
	zy reading spot and dive into your book.\\nEnjoy the quiet atmosphere of r
	eading in community.\\n\\n7:30 PM – Reading Break \\n\\nChat with your nei
	ghbor! Ask them what they are reading.\\nGrab a snack or drink at the bar\
	\nCheck out Feathered Pages' book table\\n\\n7:40 PM – Break Ends \\n\\nHe
	ad back to the Lapis Theater and do more reading.\\n\\n8:30 PM – Social Ti
	me & Book Chats \\n\\nShare thoughts on your reads\\\, favorite passages\\
	\, or just connect with fellow book lovers.\\n5 raffle winners are announc
	ed.\\n\\n9:00 PM – Event Concludes \\n \\nThis is our monthly Silent Readi
	ng Night\\\, each month we will have a new theme to inspire your reading. 
	Rediscover the joy of reading in good company at the Hugo House. \\nWe can
	’t wait to read with you! \\nFree admission to this event is made possible
	 with support from 4Culture.\n\nhttps://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-03-19/\n
	\nFrom Hugo House
URL:https://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-03-19/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:hugo-house
CATEGORIES:Hugo House
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
